    {
      "id": "sec-privacy-body",
      "type": "richText",
      "props": {
        "kicker": "",
        "body": {
          "type": "doc",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Characom Group (\"we\", \"us\") is committed to protecting the personal data of visitors to this website in accordance with Regulation (EU) 2016/679 (the General Data Protection Regulation) and the applicable data protection legislation of the Republic of Cyprus. This policy explains what we collect, why, where it is kept and the rights you hold over it."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "heading",
              "attrs": {
                "level": 2
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Who is the controller"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The data controller is Characom Group, 12 Evagorou Avenue, 1065 Nicosia, Cyprus. You can reach us about any privacy matter at info@characom.example.com, by telephone on +357 22 000 000, or by fax on +357 22 000 001."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "heading",
              "attrs": {
                "level": 2
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "What we collect and why"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "We collect personal data only when you choose to give it to us through the contact form. That data is limited to:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bulletList",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Your name and email address (required to reply to you)."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Your telephone number, if you provide it."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "The subject and message you write, and the page you sent it from."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "The date and time of your consent to this policy."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The legal basis for this processing is your consent (Article 6(1)(a) GDPR), given when you tick the consent box before submitting, and our legitimate interest in responding to business inquiries (Article 6(1)(f) GDPR). We do not use this data for marketing, we do not profile you, and we never sell it."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "heading",
              "attrs": {
                "level": 2
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Where inquiries are stored"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Inquiries submitted through this website are stored as structured records in the website's private source-code repository, hosted by GitHub, Inc. Access is restricted to authorised Characom administrators. In addition, a copy of each inquiry is delivered to our staff by email through Resend, a transactional email service that processes the message content solely to deliver the notification. Both providers act as processors under written terms; transfers outside the EEA are safeguarded by the EU Standard Contractual Clauses."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "heading",
              "attrs": {
                "level": 2
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "How long we keep it"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Inquiry records are retained for up to 24 months from your last contact with us, after which they are deleted, unless the correspondence has become part of a contract or legal matter requiring longer statutory retention."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "heading",
              "attrs": {
                "level": 2
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Your rights"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Under the GDPR you may, at any time:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bulletList",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Request access to the personal data we hold about you."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Request correction or erasure of that data."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Withdraw your consent, without affecting processing carried out before withdrawal."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Object to processing based on legitimate interest, or request restriction."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Lodge a complaint with the Office of the Commissioner for Personal Data Protection of the Republic of Cyprus."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "To exercise any of these rights, email info@characom.example.com. We respond within one month. This website also uses a small number of cookies and similar technologies, described in our Cookie Policy."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        "maxWidth": "narrow",
        "dark": false
      },
      "visible": true
    }
  ],
